safety insurance public company limited private company information  bloomberg july    pm et insurance company overview of safety insurance public company limited snapshot people company overview safety insurance public company limited provides various nonlife insurance products in thailand it offers car insurance which include compulsory motor insurance act and voluntary insurance personal accident insurance travel insurance such as travel accident insurance and home insurance including comprehensive home fire and home care insurance the company also provides small business insurance marine and transport insurance such as marine cargo insurance liability insurance of the carrier domestic cargo insurance and hull insurance and property insurance which include all risks insurance business interruption insurance in advance and fire insurance it offers its product safety insurance public company limited provides various nonlife insurance products in thailand it offers car insurance which include compulsory motor insurance act and voluntary insurance personal accident insurance travel insurance such as travel accident insurance and home insurance including comprehensive home fire and home care insurance the company also provides small business insurance marine and transport insurance such as marine cargo insurance liability insurance of the carrier domestic cargo insurance and hull insurance and property insurance which include all risks insurance business interruption insurance in advance and fire insurance it offers its products and services through agents and brokers the company was incorporated in  and is headquartered in bangkok thailand safety insurance public company limited operates as a subsidiary of nhct limited detailed description    orakarn buildingchidlom roadlumpinipathumwanbangkok  thailandfounded in  employees phone     fax     wwwsafetycoth key executives for safety insurance public company limited mr suteechai santivarakum chief executive officer pres