 safety insurance group inc is a provider of private passenger automobile insurance the company offers a portfolio of property and casualty insurance products the company is engaged in property and casualty insurance operations the companys product line includes private passenger automobile commercial automobile homeowners business owners policies personal umbrella dwelling fire commercial umbrella inland marine and watercraft the company operates through its insurance company subsidiaries safety insurance company safety indemnity insurance company and safety property and casualty insurance company private passenger automobile policies provide coverage for bodily injury and property damage to others nofault personal injury coverage for the insuredinsureds car occupants and physical damage coverage for an insureds own vehicle for collision or other perils commercial automobile policies provide coverage for bodily injury and property damage to others more from reuters » officers and directors george m murphy president chief executive officer age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance william j begley jr chief financial officer vice president secretary age  bio  compensation   reuters david e krupa vice president  claims operations age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance john patrick drago vice president  marketing age  bio  compensation   reuters james d berry vice president  underwriting age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance ann marie mckeown vice president  insurance operations age  bio  compensation   reuters paul j narciso vice president—casualty claims age  bio  compensation   reuters stephen a varga vice president  management information systems age  bio  compensation   reuters david f brussard nonexecutive chairman of the board age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance thalia meehan director bio  compensation   reuters full list on reuters » google finance beta avai