 billing charge is assessed on each bill the type of billing charge depends on the sdip points associated with the operators of each vehicle the billing charge will either be a  service fee or a  apr finance charge a late charge of  is assessed if a payment is not received by the due date you may enroll in the safety advantage program and have payments automatically withdrawn from your bank account there are no monthly billing charges when you participate in this payment program note if you have been cancelled for nonpayment during the past two years a  down payment is required homeowners personal umbrella and dwelling fire insurance your safety insurance agent can help you select one of the following billing and payment options that best suits your needs you may pay the entire premium in full at the time you apply for insurance or when your policy comes up for renewal if you choose to pay less than the full premium then you have the choice of either our  or  payment installment billing plan a billing charge of  will be assessed on all bills except for the renewal bill you may enroll in the safety advantage program and have payments automatically withdrawn from your bank account there are no monthly billing charges when you participate in this payment program business insurance your safety insurance agent can help you select the most suitable billing and payment option for your organizations needs refund policy  all policy types and combined bill regardless of the original form of payment credit account balances resulting from policy cancellations endorsements or overpayments will be refunded weekly in the form of a check mailed to the policyholders last known address addresses for mailing check payments lockbox safety insurance company po box  pittsburgh pa  premium accountingdirect for payments collected at agencies safety insurance company po box  boston ma  overnight mail  premium payments safety insurance company attention premium accounting dept pac  custom ho