ary living costs approached six figures throughout the ordeal my claims representative was patient professional and responsive i admit there were some nervous moments early on while i awaited the results of the claim investigation but in the end safety came through and fullfilled their commitment moreover i believe their reconstruction estimateappraisal was fair even generous my house had antique quartersawn pine floors they were very expensive to replace and yet safety stepped up and paid the full cost they also paid the full replacement cost for my custom kitchen cabinets and appliancesand all the rest  yeah it was a huge ordeal something i never ever want to go through again but for me safety insurance saved the day they did in a professional and timely manner what an insurance company is designed to do protect me from a huge financial loss as the result of a catastrophic eventwell done safety and thanks was this review … useful  funny  cool  matthew l south easton ma  friends  reviews share review embed review compliment send message follow matthew l stop following matthew l  ive used safety since  or so my girlfriend and i both have auto policies with them and a home owners policy ive had to use the auto policy two times and the claims were processed without issue i will say the adjuster was difficult to reach  but the body shop got paid my vehicle was fully repaired in a timely manner so i have nothing really bad to saythankfully i havent had to use the homeowners policy my brother has used them for a homeowners claim and there were no problems was this review … useful funny  cool  blessed o brockton ma  friends  reviews share review embed review compliment send message follow blessed o stop following blessed o  stay far far away from this company they are only kind to customers when there is another insurance company involved where they could get a reimbursement if your car is involved in a hit and run forget it  dont even bother reporting it to them my vehic