ies make money  that is their businessas a customer that pays all the bills on time and is not out to defraud the company i was treated as if i was a felon  phone calls went unanswered  emails were transferred to clueless representatives  well get back to you  yeah right and the checks are in the mail  the accident was in september  and it wasnt resolved until may   thats  months  it wasnt until i left a scathing facebook wall post on their wall that they contacted me  in conclusion  yes their rates as a good driver are very competitive  however safety insurance is only good until you need them  claims representatives are incompetent and downright rude  even as the victim your only effective way of getting compensated for your outofpocket costs from an accident are to lawyerupi can think of a million other things id rather do than have to call safety insurance when there is an emergency and i need help  in fact im fairly positive id get more help from an exboyfriend that i broke up with via a textmessage than the help i got from safety read more was this review … useful  funny  cool julie t tacoma wa  friends  reviews  photo share review embed review compliment send message follow julie t stop following julie t  i am really surprised by the poor reviews here as i had a fantastic experience with safety insurance and lets be honest to be thrilled with how everything worked out after youve rearended someone and crumpled the front end of your car must mean someone else did something right i went directly to the vip claims center in newton  which was still open after pm everyone there was super helpful and friendly thanks don i was able to get a rental car close to my home the very next day although i was given an estimate of two weeks for repairs including a holiday i got daily updates and the car ended up being ready two days early and looked amazing the garage that safety used in needham did a great job i will say that the cost of repairs seemed a bit high and i suspe