uge ordeal something i never ever want to go through again but for me safety insurance saved the day they did in a professional and timely manner what an insurance company is designed to do protect me from a huge financial loss as the result of a catastrophic event well done safety and thanks ive used safety since  or so my girlfriend and i both have auto policies with them and a home owners policy ive had to use the auto policy two times and the claims were processed without issue i will say the adjuster was difficult to reach but the body shop got paid my vehicle was fully repaired in a timely manner so i have nothing really bad to say thankfully i havent had to use the homeowners policy my brother has used them for a homeowners claim and there were no problems stay far far away from this company they are only kind to customers when there is another insurance company involved where they could get a reimbursement if your car is involved in a hit and run forget it  dont even bother reporting it to them my vehicle was hit while parked and my claim was denied because there was paint underneath the headlight where i was hit and they think it is latex paint from a fixed object and the appraiser they hired stated that the light broke in a different why so that means it was on when the car was damaged that is completely impossible when i was at work all day they do not want to pay because they cant get reimbursement from another insurance as they would in a regular accident i have been a customer for years paid on time and only filed one claim  and i wasnt even driving the car in that previous accident i will fight this till the end because i know that they want to avoid paying out and i will bring this to court if i have to never do business with safety insurance if you are on the road pray that you are not hit by one of their drivers although safety insurance will move your claim along quickly they will fail to keep you up to date on their personal action to one of your claims i was actually hit by one of their drivers the man swore he was an honest person and told me that i was in his blind spot however he was a liar and told the estimator false information although i cannot blame the clientele that safety insurers entirely upon them i can blame them for how they handle a claim from one of their nondrivers i specifically asked the claims adjuster if he needed pictures from the accident to expedite the claim on his side in case there was a dispute he told me we outsource that to an estimator and it is their drivers word against mine on damages so he would not need pictures when i got an estimate i asked the claims adjuster for next steps he told me to take it to an auto body shop to get fix and we will repair the damages i went to the auto body shop they agreed with the estimate from the assessors and that i would need to go through the insurance company for the rental upon doublechecking the rental policy with safety i found that they said they where  liable complete nonsense i then had to send them pictures of the skid marks pictures of the sites and pictures of the damages with my story pointbypoint the claims adjuster could have saved me a lot of time by just telling me that they found me  liable when i asked him about next steps they are an insurance company who practices are dubious to say the least if you get hit by one of their drivers make sure you call the police if the police will not showup take detailed pictures of the accident and car safety will do what ever they can not to pay you if i could give  stars i would thankfully i dont have safety insurance however a client of theirs caused a car accident with me  months ago and after the audacity of claiming it wasnt the drivers fault and sending the case to arbitration and ultimately losing im still waiting to get reimbursed for my outofpocket expenses the the person on my case at safety was matt kelly and he has ignored my emails and calls until  weeks ago when he aske